channel.title: Searching people for new project
channel.description:
Hi there,
Tittle says it all, I want to [b]start a server[/b]/source, and I need coders/testers, anyone who could be usefull. I'm looking for somewhat expirienced coders.
I don't realy matter if we start from scratch or not, but we just aren't going to c&p tut's on and on. I want this to be a [b]SPECIAL[/b] server/source, not like the hundreds of sources with a added satans isle or some sh*t like that, you get my point? I guess like thousands of people said this, but yea...
Please [i]don't spam this thread[/i], only post if your realy intrested, or just PM me.
If you've got any questions, PM me either here, or on msn(sk8ter2w8t@hotmail.com)
Thanks!
And please notice the project isn't about proving who's the best, or something. It's just all about being kind to eachother, respecting eachother. We will vote for every decision.
Accepted members :
- Hippyss - Zodi4k - Eh Pretty Easy - ASIC [hr] Denied members (+ reason):
- Joester ("I suppose if u need a good coder its me i own so if u wnt me im ok"). I hate people with big ego's (The "i own" part ;) )
